text: Xinzhuang Gymnasium () is an indoor sporting arena located in New Taipei City, Taiwan. It was built by from September 1999 until April 2002 by RSEA Engineering Corporation. ==Events== Xinzhuang Gymnasium has held many sporting events and concerts. It is also used during 2009 Summer DeaflympicsVenues - 21st Summer Deaflympics Taipei 2009 and will be used in 2017 Summer Universiade.
